      <p>Before handing anything off, I ran moderated usability tests with 5 participants to validate the core builder flows. Each session lasted about 20 minutes and followed a structured test guide. I tracked completion rate, error rate, time to success, and satisfaction level, then assigned severity ratings (1 = cosmetic, 4 = must fix) to prioritize what needed attention.</p>
